  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast and dinner are served buffet style in <strong>Restaurant 2864</strong> at the Bohinj Eco Hotel.</p>
<p>Enjoy an excellent variety of dishes - a mix of international favourites and delicious local recipes. There'll be something to keep everyone happy, adults and kids alike.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
