  <description><![CDATA[<p>Located in the lovely village of Bohinjska Bistrica - a 10-minute bus journey from <a data-udi="umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753}" title="Lake Bohinj">Lake Bohinj</a> - the Bohinj-ECO is a family-friendly hotel with an environmental conscience. The hotel is modern and comfortable with spacious rooms and picturesque views, providing a tranquil retreat for your stay.</p>
<h2>Explore the picturesque village and scenic trails</h2>
<p>Browse the shops and sample local treats from the bakery. There are scenic walking trails right on your doorstep and it's just 10 minutes by bus to Lake Bohinj. The hotel is also conveniently close to the train station - hop on board and enjoy the picturesque journey to Nova Gorica and Bled.</p>
<h2>Excellent pool and spa facilities</h2>
<p>A paradise for families - the connected Aquapark has everything the children need for a good time and is great for adults too - swim in the pools, enjoying soothing whirlpools and water jets. Crank up the adrenaline and take the wild river, or try over-water bouldering. There's also plenty of quiet spots if you're seeking a bit of rest and relaxation - head to the panoramic wellness area in the main hotel, which is reserved for over 18s and has a beautiful indoor pool, saunas and a steam room. You also get one free entry to the sauna park that's part of the Aquapark. You won't need to leave the hotel to have fun, but with tonnes of adventures to enjoy nearby, we recommend you do.</p>
<p>Standing out for sustainable practices, the hotel uses geothermal heating and smart systems to manage energy use and waste.</p>]]></description>
