  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Spa &amp; wellness facilities</strong></p>
<p>The hotel has a panoramic in-house wellness area that is open to over 18s only. Reservation is required due to limited space, and facilities include:</p>
<ul>
<li>Indoor swimming pool</li>
<li>Steam room</li>
<li>Sauna</li>
<li>Relaxation area</li>
<li>Spa and massage treatments (payable locally)</li>
<li>Pool towels</li>
</ul>
<p>In addition to this, guests have unlimited use of swimming pools (indoor and outdoor) at the family-friendly <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.bohinj-eco-hotel.si/aquapark/" target="_blank">Aquapark</a> (connected to the hotel), and one free entrance per person to the sauna park there (outdoor pools open from 1 Jul - 31 Aug, weather permitting).</p>
<p><strong>Additional facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Parking</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Family facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Cots &amp; linen available (approx €10/night)</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
